name: Boitatá
description:
Known as a great snake of fire. It protects animals and forests from people who do them harm and, above all, who carry out fires in the forests.

This snake can transform itself into a burning log in order to deceive and burn the invaders and destroyers of the forests. It is believed that the person who looks at Boitatá becomes blind and crazy.<Crypto Legends | A Series by Renancio Monte | 2021>
